    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入我们的游戏讨论群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家群：548253790 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如加群时提示群已满，欢迎加入2群 ：996760787 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们期望听到你的声音!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/c9b15ff8f9f5fecfa2e8be9c9443a297.avif?t=1768943414\" width=1530 height=378 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款 2D 平台动作 Boss Rush 游戏，专注于高速、精准、极具张力的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抓住与鬼交锋的每个瞬息，斩击、格挡、治疗乃至消耗灵魂释放樱侍的特殊能力——每一次出手皆关乎生死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗后，自由选择下一个世界与成长方式。更强大的樱侍，往往会吸引更凶恶的鬼。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>招架</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/7c5716e66f551c91942eada454c10b15.poster.avif?t=1768943414\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/7c5716e66f551c91942eada454c10b15.webm?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/7c5716e66f551c91942eada454c10b15.mp4?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终结技</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/45b88db55630fa278e15b2b0ce88ba22.poster.avif?t=1768943414\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/45b88db55630fa278e15b2b0ce88ba22.webm?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/45b88db55630fa278e15b2b0ce88ba22.mp4?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>御守</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/63e87050711bcadda72b21cc4e57f158.poster.avif?t=1768943414\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/63e87050711bcadda72b21cc4e57f158.webm?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/63e87050711bcadda72b21cc4e57f158.mp4?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/a6f2895be8b140c58e1134d8df08b7ee.poster.avif?t=1768943414\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/a6f2895be8b140c58e1134d8df08b7ee.webm?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008640/extras/a6f2895be8b140c58e1134d8df08b7ee.mp4?t=1768943414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特机制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当鬼被封印，它的魂魄将被“樱藏”转化并为你所用。这股力量会化作御守，用以强化天才不同的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗前随心搭配御守，让你重新定义战斗方式，击败曾经看似没有破绽的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专注招架反击还是嗜血强攻，或者强化灵力以距离建立优势…… 没有绝对的最强，唯有最契合你的斩鬼之道。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从“鬼”从地狱苏醒，灾厄席卷人间。即使被击败，它们的灵魂仍会回归躯体，继续作恶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝望之中，一株以恶鬼魂魄为养料，能将其封印的神圣之樱 「樱藏」破土而生。你叫「天才」，人神共鸣的末代樱侍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自诞生起便与神树同息，手中利刃即是世界的解药。斩鬼夺魂，化其力量为己用，在轮回死战中终结鬼神灾祸。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>艺术风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《樱侍》的视觉表现以高帧率和风像素画为基调，融合古典和风美学与末世氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗场景都以不同主题呈现：神社废墟、战场荒原、染血樱林……同样的，每只鬼都承载着各自的传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >繁盛的「樱藏」树下，唯有你的刀，能决定这片土地的命运。</p>",
